{
  "3307120": {
    "name": "Kitty Powers' Matchmaker Makeover",
    "steam_appid": 3307120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307120/extras/c222c02bc6d0bae4a62d79b12cdef31f.avif?t=1770898272\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's time to make love happen, again!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step back into the role of trainee matchmaker, and help quirky clients find their perfect match, all under the 'expert' supervision of British Drag Queen and matchmaking maven, Kitty Powers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you restore her neglected dating agencies to their full potential?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you become a Matchmaking Maestro?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This remastered version has been rebuilt from the ground up and features vibrant new artwork, expanded customization options, and a host of gameplay improvements to make matchmaking even more fun and inclusive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307120/extras/170fece8601ddef66c0f02aefbcf1d09.avif?t=1770898272\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhanced Artwork:</strong> Feast your eyes on Matchmaker’s enhanced assets and sumptuously high definition artwork. Now with 4K and ultra-widescreen modes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >N<strong>ew and Improved Mini-games:</strong> Tackle four brand new dating dilemmas including ‘Fling the Food’, ‘Rose or Knickers’ and ‘Divide the Dessert’, as well as numerous improved minigames from the original!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New and Expanded Game Mechanics:</strong> Get to grips with new mechanics such as ‘Chemistry’ and ‘Juicy Secrets’ to take your matchmaking to new heights!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expanded Customization:</strong> Players have new options to dress and style their characters, with updated personalities and fashion that ensures anything goes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More Diversity:</strong> Choose from male, female and non-binary characters, who can be straight, gay, bisexual or pansexual!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Salon Makeover:</strong> Meet your new personal stylist, who will help you spruce up your characters up for their big night with upgradeable salon treatments!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Return of Kitty Powers:</strong> The iconic drag queen is back with her signature witty commentary, guiding players on their matchmaking journey! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
